1
00:00:17,500 --> 00:00:19,500
Bloodstain.

2
00:00:21,500 --> 00:00:22,500
You did this behind me?

3
00:00:23,500 --> 00:00:25,500
What are you doing in my room?

4
00:00:25,500 --> 00:00:26,500
Yang.

5
00:00:26,700 --> 00:00:28,500
You should beware of this man.

6
00:00:28,800 --> 00:00:30,500
I feel like this man is dangerous.

7
00:00:30,800 --> 00:00:31,500
He's hiding something from us.

8
00:00:32,500 --> 00:00:36,500
Maybe if he sleeps with a girl, he might like it.

9
00:00:36,800 --> 00:00:38,500
But if we put the orchid dust in the cicada,

10
00:00:39,200 --> 00:00:42,500
it will become cicada orchids with arousal property.

11
00:00:42,800 --> 00:00:46,500
Doctor Qi leaving the house like this, they must have a plan.

12
00:00:46,800 --> 00:00:48,500
But it's good for us.

13
00:00:48,800 --> 00:00:50,500
It's the right time to make cicada orchids.

14
00:00:50,800 --> 00:00:53,500
When the dust flies to catch the cicada,

15
00:00:53,800 --> 00:00:57,500
it will make them breed like crazy.

16
00:00:57,900 --> 00:00:59,500
In order to find the strong one that survived.

17
00:01:00,500 --> 00:01:04,500
The weak cicadas will not be able to withstand the effects of the orchid dust

18
00:01:04,800 --> 00:01:05,500
and eventually died.

19
00:01:06,500 --> 00:01:10,500
After that, we wait for the mushroom to grow out of its body.

20
00:01:11,500 --> 00:01:13,500
Why is the cicada making such a loud noise?

21
00:03:06,500 --> 00:03:07,500
Burn them all.

22
00:03:07,700 --> 00:03:08,500
Yes, Madam.

23
00:03:42,500 --> 00:03:43,500
Li.

24
00:03:44,500 --> 00:03:45,500
What's going on?

25
00:03:47,500 --> 00:03:50,500
The cicadas are infected, so they all died.

26
00:03:51,500 --> 00:03:54,500
But I ordered the workers to burn them.

27
00:03:54,700 --> 00:03:55,500
Don't worry.

28
00:05:21,500 --> 00:05:22,500
Excuse me.

29
00:05:23,500 --> 00:05:24,500
Sorry.

30
00:05:35,500 --> 00:05:36,500
Mei.

31
00:05:37,500 --> 00:05:38,500
Mei.

32
00:05:40,500 --> 00:05:42,500
Fu, why is Mei like this?

33
00:05:43,500 --> 00:05:44,500
I don't know either.

34
00:05:45,500 --> 00:05:47,500
She has been like this for a while now.

35
00:05:47,700 --> 00:05:51,500
She stays in bed all day, and gets up and play with me once in a while.

36
00:05:52,500 --> 00:05:54,500
But she didn't feel sick like before.

37
00:06:00,500 --> 00:06:02,500
And how are you here?

38
00:06:03,500 --> 00:06:06,500
We have food every meal

39
00:06:07,500 --> 00:06:09,500
but we're not as happy as when we were at home.

40
00:06:10,500 --> 00:06:13,500
When will we go back to our home?

41
00:06:14,500 --> 00:06:16,500
Let me accomplish an important task first.

42
00:06:16,700 --> 00:06:18,500
Wait a little longer.

43
00:06:22,500 --> 00:06:25,500
Have you met Tian lately?

44
00:06:26,500 --> 00:06:27,500
Why do you ask?

45
00:06:29,500 --> 00:06:30,500
Well...

46
00:06:37,500 --> 00:06:38,500
Do you see?

47
00:06:39,500 --> 00:06:42,500
That I take care of your siblings and let them live comfortably.

48
00:06:43,500 --> 00:06:45,500
I provide both food and medicine.

49
00:06:45,800 --> 00:06:47,500
Don't worry about anything.

50
00:06:48,500 --> 00:06:49,500
Just do your job.

51
00:06:54,500 --> 00:06:55,500
Right?

52
00:07:10,500 --> 00:07:15,500
From what you told me, Big Brother doesn't trust Li anymore.

53
00:07:16,500 --> 00:07:19,500
He must have believed that Li had killed someone

54
00:07:20,500 --> 00:07:22,500
to conceal Tian's secret.

55
00:07:23,500 --> 00:07:25,500
I think that what it is.

56
00:07:25,900 --> 00:07:28,500
Otherwise, Doctor Qi wouldn't be invited to investigate the strange herbs and mushroom.

57
00:07:30,500 --> 00:07:31,500
Li is decisive.

58
00:07:32,500 --> 00:07:36,500
But I didn't think that she could be this cruel.

59
00:07:38,500 --> 00:07:39,500
If she can kill,

60
00:07:40,500 --> 00:07:45,500
it means Tian's secret must be very important, very serious.

61
00:07:47,500 --> 00:07:51,500
So have you seen anything suspicious about his secret?

62
00:07:52,500 --> 00:07:53,500
Not yet.

63
00:07:54,500 --> 00:07:56,500
But I came today because a strange thing happened last night.

64
00:08:11,500 --> 00:08:13,500
Last night, the cicadas made loud noises throughout the house.

65
00:08:14,500 --> 00:08:15,500
Why is that strange?

66
00:08:17,500 --> 00:08:19,500
It's strange because its noises were louder than I've heard before.

67
00:08:20,500 --> 00:08:22,500
And by the next morning, they were all dead.

68
00:08:23,500 --> 00:08:27,500
Then Madam Li ordered the workers to tidy up and burn the remains.

69
00:08:27,800 --> 00:08:28,500
Saying that it was because of an insect disease.

70
00:08:30,500 --> 00:08:34,500
But from what I see, it’s not, so I collected its remain to let you check it.

71
00:09:08,500 --> 00:09:09,500
Jiu. Jiu.

72
00:09:10,500 --> 00:09:11,500
Fu, I'm going back now, what's up?

73
00:09:12,500 --> 00:09:13,500
Yes, about Tian.

74
00:09:22,500 --> 00:09:23,500
What's about Tian?

75
00:09:24,500 --> 00:09:25,500
I heard Mr. Ma talking to someone.

76
00:09:25,800 --> 00:09:28,500
He said that he sent a guy to Tian's house.

77
00:09:30,500 --> 00:09:32,500
You must warn Tian.

78
00:09:32,900 --> 00:09:36,500
Don't let those bad guy hurt him.

79
00:09:38,500 --> 00:09:41,500
If I could, I would like to protect Tian from those evil bastards.

80
00:09:42,500 --> 00:09:43,500
Please do it instead of me.

81
00:09:44,500 --> 00:09:46,500
Get rid of those wicked bastards.

82
00:10:10,500 --> 00:10:14,500
We have managed to burn all the weak cicadas already.

83
00:10:15,500 --> 00:10:18,500
I'm going out to find the strong cicada

84
00:10:18,800 --> 00:10:21,500
that survived from the power of orchid dust tonight.

85
00:10:22,500 --> 00:10:26,500
Soon we will have the cicada orchid ready to be used.

86
00:11:21,500 --> 00:11:25,500
This is the strongest cicada.

87
00:12:10,500 --> 00:12:11,500
Who are you?

88
00:12:13,500 --> 00:12:14,500
Tian.

89
00:12:44,500 --> 00:12:46,500
Or is it Mr. Ma's subordinate?

90
00:12:47,500 --> 00:12:48,500
Tian.

91
00:13:10,500 --> 00:13:12,500
Tian, Tian.

92
00:13:15,500 --> 00:13:16,500
Tian.

93
00:13:17,500 --> 00:13:18,500
Tian.

94
00:13:19,500 --> 00:13:20,500
Tian.

95
00:13:21,500 --> 00:13:22,500
Tian.

96
00:13:23,500 --> 00:13:24,500
Jiu.

97
00:13:26,500 --> 00:13:27,500
Tian.

98
00:13:29,500 --> 00:13:30,500
Are you okay?

99
00:13:41,500 --> 00:13:42,500
I'm really worried about you.

100
00:13:46,500 --> 00:13:47,500
Hey.

101
00:13:50,500 --> 00:13:51,500
I am fine.

102
00:13:53,500 --> 00:13:55,500
Why did you come into my room?

103
00:13:57,500 --> 00:13:59,500
I saw a stranger entering the house.

104
00:14:00,500 --> 00:14:02,500
I'm afraid he will hurt you.

105
00:14:03,500 --> 00:14:05,500
So you're alright?

106
00:14:06,500 --> 00:14:07,500
Nobody hurt you, right?

107
00:14:12,500 --> 00:14:13,500
And what is this?

108
00:14:18,500 --> 00:14:19,500
Paint.

109
00:14:20,500 --> 00:14:23,500
I dropped it when I was painting.

110
00:14:32,500 --> 00:14:33,500
Paint?

111
00:14:39,500 --> 00:14:42,500
If you're alright, I'll leave.

112
00:14:48,500 --> 00:14:49,500
I'm glad…

113
00:14:52,500 --> 00:14:53,500
that you are worried about me.

114
00:14:55,500 --> 00:14:57,500
I thought you were still mad at me.

115
00:14:58,500 --> 00:14:59,500
I'm not mad at you.

116
00:15:03,500 --> 00:15:05,500
If you are not angry with me,

117
00:15:07,500 --> 00:15:11,500
from today,

118
00:15:14,500 --> 00:15:15,500
let's study as usual.

119
00:15:39,500 --> 00:15:40,500
See you tomorrow.

120
00:16:48,500 --> 00:16:49,500
It's me.

121
00:16:53,500 --> 00:16:57,500
What's wrong with you, Jia? Who injured you?

122
00:16:59,500 --> 00:17:00,500
It's Jiu.

123
00:17:01,500 --> 00:17:04,500
But don't worry. He didn't know it was me.

124
00:17:05,500 --> 00:17:06,500
Jiu?

125
00:17:07,500 --> 00:17:09,500
The man that Tian accepted for work?

126
00:17:10,500 --> 00:17:11,500
Yes, Madam.

127
00:17:12,500 --> 00:17:13,500
I think this guy looks suspicious.

128
00:17:14,500 --> 00:17:18,500
He's agile, good at fighting. He's not like an ordinary worker.

129
00:17:19,500 --> 00:17:20,500
Keep an eye on him.

130
00:17:23,500 --> 00:17:25,500
So did you get the cicada that survived?

131
00:17:26,500 --> 00:17:27,500
Yes, Madam.

132
00:17:41,500 --> 00:17:42,500
Soon.

133
00:17:44,500 --> 00:17:48,500
We will get cicada orchid to make arousal drug.

134
00:17:49,200 --> 00:17:49,500
Good.

135
00:17:50,500 --> 00:17:54,500
When Tian has a wife and children and becomes the head of the association,

136
00:17:55,500 --> 00:17:57,500
that day, I can die in peace.

137
00:18:31,500 --> 00:18:35,500
You are nimble, not like other workers.

138
00:18:36,500 --> 00:18:38,500
What did you do before staying here?

139
00:18:39,500 --> 00:18:41,500
Why are you asking?

140
00:18:42,500 --> 00:18:44,500
Mr. Tian is the heir of the Song Family.

141
00:18:45,500 --> 00:18:47,500
Besides the people who come to seek benefits,

142
00:18:48,500 --> 00:18:49,500
he's also a target of murder.

143
00:19:04,500 --> 00:19:05,500
You.

144
00:19:06,500 --> 00:19:08,500
I have to beware those who come close to Mr. Tian.

145
00:19:09,500 --> 00:19:10,500
And you,

146
00:19:11,500 --> 00:19:13,500
If you want to stay here for a long time, don't be so inquisitive.

147
00:19:31,500 --> 00:19:34,500
They have been discussing for a long time.

148
00:19:35,500 --> 00:19:38,500
Or do they not like my land?

149
00:19:39,000 --> 00:19:40,500
Is it too expensive? Should I give them a discount?

150
00:19:41,500 --> 00:19:44,500
No, if you offer discount, you won't get enough money to buy back the palace.

151
00:19:51,500 --> 00:19:52,500
Do you like it?

152
00:19:53,500 --> 00:19:58,500
Yes, but I think the price is too high.

153
00:19:58,800 --> 00:20:02,500
I just took a look at the land nearby.

154
00:20:02,900 --> 00:20:04,500
It's cheaper than yours for a hundred thousand.

155
00:20:05,500 --> 00:20:09,500
But mine is right next to the river.

156
00:20:10,000 --> 00:20:11,500
Most importantly, there will be a road running through the land.

157
00:20:12,000 --> 00:20:13,500
You should probably heard the news as well.

158
00:20:14,500 --> 00:20:17,500
But I don't quite like the land next to the river.

159
00:20:18,500 --> 00:20:20,500
I'm not partial to water.

160
00:20:21,100 --> 00:20:24,500
But if you give lower the price a bit more,

161
00:20:25,500 --> 00:20:26,500
I will buy it right away.

162
00:20:31,500 --> 00:20:33,500
Sorry for being late.

163
00:20:37,500 --> 00:20:41,500
Madam, are you making an appointment with another customer as well?

164
00:20:44,500 --> 00:20:47,500
Do you guys come to look at the land too?

165
00:20:47,800 --> 00:20:49,500
Yes, and this is my boss.

166
00:20:50,500 --> 00:20:52,500
He's very interested in this land.

167
00:20:53,500 --> 00:20:54,500
Right, Sir?

168
00:20:55,500 --> 00:20:56,500
Yes.

169
00:20:58,500 --> 00:21:01,500
He's looking for a place in Bang Pa-in

170
00:21:02,000 --> 00:21:03,500
to build a vacation home.

171
00:21:04,200 --> 00:21:07,500
And most importantly, the land here is very beautiful.

172
00:21:08,000 --> 00:21:09,500
The atmosphere is also good, next to the river.

173
00:21:10,500 --> 00:21:12,500
She's selling very cheaply.

174
00:21:13,200 --> 00:21:15,500
I thought my boss would have missed this place.

175
00:21:16,500 --> 00:21:20,500
I hope that you haven't sold the land to other customers yet.

176
00:21:21,500 --> 00:21:22,500
You can't, Madam.

177
00:21:23,500 --> 00:21:26,500
I've been here first. You have to give me the chance first.

178
00:21:27,500 --> 00:21:30,500
But my boss offers you four hundred thousand, Madam.

179
00:21:31,500 --> 00:21:32,500
Four hundred twenty thousand.

180
00:21:33,500 --> 00:21:34,500
I give you four hundred fifty thousand.

181
00:21:35,500 --> 00:21:36,500
Four hundred thousand...

182
00:21:36,900 --> 00:21:37,500
Come here. / What?

183
00:21:39,500 --> 00:21:42,500
Yang, that's enough.

184
00:21:43,000 --> 00:21:43,500
If they don't take it, we'll be in trouble.

185
00:21:44,500 --> 00:21:45,500
Come on, I'll take care of it myself.

186
00:21:47,000 --> 00:21:47,500
Madam.

187
00:21:49,500 --> 00:21:51,500
My brother said it was too little.

188
00:21:53,500 --> 00:21:54,500
Five hundred thousand is better.

189
00:21:58,500 --> 00:21:59,500
If you want the land at five hundred thousand,

190
00:22:00,500 --> 00:22:01,500
you can take it, sir.

191
00:22:10,500 --> 00:22:11,500
Yang.

192
00:22:12,500 --> 00:22:14,500
It's normal for new millionaires.

193
00:22:15,500 --> 00:22:17,500
How can you compete with my boss?

194
00:22:19,500 --> 00:22:20,500
Let's make a contract, Madam.

195
00:22:22,500 --> 00:22:23,500
I give you six hundred thousand.

196
00:22:34,500 --> 00:22:35,500
Wow.

197
00:22:37,500 --> 00:22:39,500
Thanks a lot, Yang.

198
00:22:40,500 --> 00:22:44,500
If it wasn't you and Tian, I still probably couldn't sell the land and wouldn't get this price.

199
00:22:45,500 --> 00:22:48,500
Even if you couldn't sell, I will help you until you sell it anyway.

200
00:22:49,500 --> 00:22:53,500
And your land is about to have a road running through. Many people want it.

201
00:22:56,500 --> 00:22:58,500
But I'm a bit sad.

202
00:22:59,000 --> 00:23:02,500
It's like I sold the lands of my ancestors for money.

203
00:23:03,000 --> 00:23:03,500
I destroy the treasures.

204
00:23:04,500 --> 00:23:07,500
Don't worry too much, your ancestors must be happy

205
00:23:08,500 --> 00:23:09,500
that their wealth has helped the children.

206
00:23:10,500 --> 00:23:11,500
Really?

207
00:23:19,500 --> 00:23:24,500
You suddenly turned your face away from me and sighed. What does it mean?

208
00:23:25,500 --> 00:23:27,500
Even though I and Tian break off the engagement,

209
00:23:28,500 --> 00:23:31,500
what about you and me?

210
00:23:35,500 --> 00:23:37,500
What is it between you and me?

211
00:23:42,500 --> 00:23:44,500
I'm kidding.

212
00:23:45,500 --> 00:23:47,500
Hey, don’t worry.

213
00:23:48,500 --> 00:23:51,500
I know that we still have many problems ahead of us.

214
00:23:52,500 --> 00:23:55,500
I know because I'm your ex-fiancé's brother.

215
00:23:55,800 --> 00:23:56,500
But don't worry.

216
00:23:57,500 --> 00:24:01,500
I believe that we can go through all these problems.

217
00:24:02,500 --> 00:24:03,500
Believe me.

218
00:24:04,500 --> 00:24:08,500
Let's eat cake.

219
00:24:09,500 --> 00:24:10,500
Thanks.

220
00:24:12,500 --> 00:24:14,500
Tian is back. The desserts are here.

221
00:24:15,500 --> 00:24:16,500
Sit down, bro.

222
00:24:18,500 --> 00:24:22,500
Wow, you bought a lot of books.

223
00:24:23,500 --> 00:24:26,500
I want Jiu to practice reading a lot so that he can be fluent.

224
00:24:27,500 --> 00:24:30,500
Jiu, the one you said that he seemed to be mad at you?

225
00:24:31,500 --> 00:24:33,500
So how is it?

226
00:24:34,500 --> 00:24:37,500
I am worried about myself and let you help me a lot.

227
00:24:38,500 --> 00:24:39,500
We understand each other well now.

228
00:24:43,500 --> 00:24:44,500
Let's eat.

229
00:24:46,500 --> 00:24:48,500
My love.

230
00:24:49,500 --> 00:24:52,500
I'd like two more plates, please.

231
00:25:00,500 --> 00:25:01,500
What?

232
00:25:01,900 --> 00:25:04,500
What do you mean that you will not marry Tian?

233
00:25:04,800 --> 00:25:05,500
Right, Father.

234
00:25:06,500 --> 00:25:09,500
After we get the money, we'll pay the debt to Aunt Li.

235
00:25:10,500 --> 00:25:12,500
And it's done.

236
00:25:12,800 --> 00:25:15,500
How can you do this all of a sudden?

237
00:25:16,000 --> 00:25:18,500
If they find out, I'll lose credibility.

238
00:25:19,500 --> 00:25:22,500
I already told you that I didn't want to get married.

239
00:25:23,500 --> 00:25:24,500
I don't love Tian.

240
00:25:24,800 --> 00:25:27,500
But he is a good man.

241
00:25:28,500 --> 00:25:29,500
But I still don't love him anyway.

242
00:25:30,500 --> 00:25:33,500
I don't want to be with someone I don't love, Father.

243
00:25:34,500 --> 00:25:35,500
You'll love each other eventually.

244
00:25:36,500 --> 00:25:38,500
No, I can't love anyone else.

245
00:25:38,900 --> 00:25:39,500
Huh?

246
00:25:40,500 --> 00:25:44,500
What do you mean? Do you already have someone you love?

247
00:25:46,500 --> 00:25:47,500
Nangnoi.

248
00:25:48,500 --> 00:25:51,500
Tell me now who is this man?

249
00:25:52,000 --> 00:25:52,500
Where is he?

250
00:25:55,500 --> 00:25:57,500
I won't tell you.

251
00:25:58,000 --> 00:25:59,500
And if you still force me to do this,

252
00:26:00,500 --> 00:26:01,500
I will run away.

253
00:26:12,500 --> 00:26:13,500
It's here.

254
00:26:22,500 --> 00:26:24,500
Five hundred sacks of rice.

255
00:26:25,000 --> 00:26:25,500
Five hundred sacks.

256
00:26:33,500 --> 00:26:35,500
Your handwriting has become more beautiful.

257
00:26:36,500 --> 00:26:38,500
But the number five is not written like this.

258
00:26:41,500 --> 00:26:42,500
It's written like this.

259
00:27:02,500 --> 00:27:04,500
I'm sorry, I can't remember.

260
00:27:05,500 --> 00:27:06,500
It's okay.

261
00:27:07,500 --> 00:27:10,500
In the past, I wrote things in the wrong way as well.

262
00:27:11,500 --> 00:27:13,500
My handwriting is a lot worse than yours right now.

263
00:27:21,500 --> 00:27:22,500
Father.

264
00:27:29,500 --> 00:27:32,500
I'm checking the accounts.

265
00:27:32,900 --> 00:27:34,500
Do you want anything?

266
00:27:39,500 --> 00:27:40,500
No.

267
00:27:41,500 --> 00:27:42,500
I just came to check.

268
00:27:43,500 --> 00:27:44,500
Go ahead.

269
00:27:46,500 --> 00:27:47,500
Yes, Father.

270
00:27:54,500 --> 00:27:55,500
Li.

271
00:27:56,500 --> 00:28:00,500
Do you know anything about the new worker named Jiu?

272
00:28:00,800 --> 00:28:02,500
Who is he? Where does he come from?

273
00:28:03,500 --> 00:28:05,500
Why? What's the matter?

274
00:28:08,500 --> 00:28:10,500
Why are you shocked?

275
00:28:11,500 --> 00:28:12,500
What's the problem?

276
00:28:13,500 --> 00:28:14,500
I just asked about a worker.

277
00:28:15,500 --> 00:28:20,500
I wasn't shocked. I'm just surprised that you ask me.

278
00:28:21,500 --> 00:28:23,500
So do you know or not?

279
00:28:24,500 --> 00:28:27,500
I don't know who he is.

280
00:28:28,500 --> 00:28:31,500
I only knew that he had saved Tian's life.

281
00:28:33,500 --> 00:28:36,500
Usually you know everything about Tian.

282
00:28:37,500 --> 00:28:39,500
Even his secret,

283
00:28:39,800 --> 00:28:41,500
you also know that, right?

284
00:28:44,500 --> 00:28:47,500
Despite your sarcastic remark,

285
00:28:47,900 --> 00:28:49,500
it didn't make me know more than you.

286
00:29:11,500 --> 00:29:13,500
Zhang, Zhang.

287
00:29:15,500 --> 00:29:17,500
Zhang, Zhang.

288
00:29:18,500 --> 00:29:25,500
I wish you know the pain that I got.

289
00:29:25,800 --> 00:29:26,500
Zhang.

290
00:29:27,500 --> 00:29:28,500
Zhang.

291
00:29:34,500 --> 00:29:35,500
Tian.

292
00:29:36,500 --> 00:29:37,500
I'm sorry.

293
00:29:38,500 --> 00:29:39,500
What happened?

294
00:29:40,500 --> 00:29:41,500
I'm a homosexual.

295
00:29:42,500 --> 00:29:44,500
No, it can't be true.

296
00:29:45,500 --> 00:29:46,500
Tian.

297
00:29:48,500 --> 00:29:53,500
I hope that someday you will experience the pain that I had suffered.

298
00:29:54,000 --> 00:29:55,500
You will understand how I feel.

299
00:29:55,800 --> 00:29:56,500
Zhang.

300
00:29:57,500 --> 00:29:59,500
Tian, this is not true.

301
00:29:59,800 --> 00:30:02,500
It shouldn't be you. Not you. Tian!

302
00:30:03,500 --> 00:30:04,500
Tian.

303
00:30:05,500 --> 00:30:06,500
Tian.

304
00:30:07,500 --> 00:30:08,500
Tian.

305
00:30:12,500 --> 00:30:13,500
Tian.

306
00:30:26,500 --> 00:30:29,500
(Blessing)

307
00:30:30,500 --> 00:30:31,500
Amen.

308
00:30:38,500 --> 00:30:41,500
Why did you wake up early today to offer food to the monks with me?

309
00:30:45,500 --> 00:30:47,500
I'm a sinner.

310
00:30:48,500 --> 00:30:50,500
I usually don’t go to the temple to make merit.

311
00:30:51,500 --> 00:30:52,500
When I decided to make one,

312
00:30:54,500 --> 00:30:55,500
it seems strange.

313
00:30:57,500 --> 00:30:59,500
It's not what I mean, Sir.

314
00:31:00,000 --> 00:31:02,500
I saw your face didn't look good, so I ask you this.

315
00:31:02,900 --> 00:31:04,500
Are you not feeling well?

316
00:31:07,500 --> 00:31:10,500
Maybe I'm really a sinner.

317
00:31:11,500 --> 00:31:13,500
Why do you think that?

318
00:31:14,200 --> 00:31:16,500
That time, I didn't protect Zhang.

319
00:31:17,500 --> 00:31:19,500
So he decided to end his life.

320
00:31:21,000 --> 00:31:24,500
I'm afraid that this sin will go to my children instead.

321
00:31:29,500 --> 00:31:32,500
A bad premonition happened because you felt guilty for Mr. Zhang.

322
00:31:33,500 --> 00:31:35,500
Mr. Tian and Mr. Yang both are boys.

323
00:31:36,500 --> 00:31:39,500
Even though they are targeted, they'll be safe eventually.

324
00:31:40,500 --> 00:31:43,500
But if you still feels uneasy,

325
00:31:44,200 --> 00:31:46,500
let's find a day to make merit at the temple.

326
00:31:47,500 --> 00:31:48,500
So you will be more at ease.

327
00:31:53,500 --> 00:31:56,500
Since I let Jiu work for me, he can help me a lot.

328
00:31:57,500 --> 00:31:59,500
Even though he can't write and read,

329
00:32:00,000 --> 00:32:01,500
he is determined and is quick-witted.

330
00:32:02,500 --> 00:32:03,500
I think he will be fluent soon.

331
00:32:07,500 --> 00:32:08,500
Jiu is really talented.

332
00:32:12,500 --> 00:32:13,500
What about his family?

333
00:32:14,500 --> 00:32:16,500
His parents are dead.

334
00:32:17,000 --> 00:32:19,500
He only has two younger siblings left. They are now living with a relative.

335
00:32:19,500 --> 00:32:21,500
That's all.

336
00:32:23,500 --> 00:32:25,500
And what about his wife?

337
00:32:26,500 --> 00:32:27,500
He doesn't have one.

338
00:32:28,500 --> 00:32:29,500
He's fine-looking.

339
00:32:31,500 --> 00:32:32,500
Why doesn't he have a wife?

340
00:32:35,500 --> 00:32:37,500
Why do you ask about Jiu?

341
00:32:39,500 --> 00:32:43,500
I saw that he worked closely with you,

342
00:32:45,500 --> 00:32:49,500
so I want to know his background.

343
00:32:50,500 --> 00:32:51,500
Can you trust him?

344
00:32:53,500 --> 00:32:54,500
Don't worry.

345
00:32:55,500 --> 00:32:58,500
I can trust him, he saved my life once.

346
00:33:06,500 --> 00:33:07,500
Keep working.

347
00:33:31,500 --> 00:33:33,500
Bang Pa-in land, 30 rai, for sale.

348
00:33:38,500 --> 00:33:41,500
30 Rai.

349
00:33:51,500 --> 00:33:54,500
Jia, Mr. Song asked me about Jiu as if he suspected.

350
00:33:55,200 --> 00:33:56,500
My heart almost stopped.

351
00:33:57,500 --> 00:34:00,500
I thought he saw Tian and Jiu were close to each other like I saw.

352
00:34:01,500 --> 00:34:04,500
Does your cicada orchid still not work?

353
00:34:05,500 --> 00:34:08,500
Not yet. Last night, I sneaked in to check,

354
00:34:08,900 --> 00:34:09,500
but it was still normal.

355
00:34:10,500 --> 00:34:13,500
If we don't rush Tian to sleep with women,

356
00:34:14,000 --> 00:34:15,500
I'm afraid that the secret will be exposed first.

357
00:34:33,500 --> 00:34:34,500
Finally, Madam.

358
00:34:35,500 --> 00:34:38,500
The mushroom is about to pierce through the cicadas.

359
00:34:42,500 --> 00:34:43,500
It's almost ready.

360
00:34:50,500 --> 00:34:53,500
Tian's wedding day is getting closer, Sir.

361
00:34:54,000 --> 00:34:55,500
If we're late, we'll all be in trouble.

362
00:34:56,500 --> 00:34:59,500
My son would have lost hope of inheriting.

363
00:35:01,500 --> 00:35:04,500
You will also be oppressed by Tian.

364
00:35:05,500 --> 00:35:06,500
I can't stay calm as well.

365
00:35:08,500 --> 00:35:10,500
But my man is doing his job.

366
00:35:10,900 --> 00:35:13,500
Did he send you news?

367
00:35:14,000 --> 00:35:16,500
Who is he? Tell me please, so I can…

368
00:35:56,500 --> 00:35:57,500
The cicada is not dead..

369
00:35:58,500 --> 00:35:59,500
What cicada?

370
00:36:00,500 --> 00:36:03,500
My man collected this for me the other day.

371
00:36:04,500 --> 00:36:08,500
Is there something strange about cicadas at your house?

372
00:36:11,500 --> 00:36:14,500
My subordinate is suspicious that the cicada

373
00:36:15,500 --> 00:36:16,500
is related to the strange orchid.

374
00:36:32,000 --> 00:36:34,500
The person sent to investigate about Jiu has already got some news for us.

375
00:36:34,500 --> 00:36:37,500
He is a seller of sugar craft near the shrine.

376
00:36:38,500 --> 00:36:39,500
He has two siblings.

377
00:36:40,200 --> 00:36:41,500
His parents are all dead just like Mr. Tian said.

378
00:36:45,500 --> 00:36:46,500
But there is still a doubt.

379
00:36:48,500 --> 00:36:49,500
What's the matter?

380
00:36:49,800 --> 00:36:52,300
The house that Jiu used to live in was in the area of Mr. Ma.

381
00:36:53,300 --> 00:36:56,300
The locals have seen he went there as well.

382
00:36:58,300 --> 00:36:59,300
This means...

383
00:37:01,300 --> 00:37:03,300
Jiu is Ma's subordinate?

384
00:37:05,300 --> 00:37:07,300
Did Ma send him to hurt Tian?

385
00:37:08,300 --> 00:37:10,300
I'm not sure about it, Sir.

386
00:37:11,300 --> 00:37:12,300
We can investigate until here.

387
00:37:13,300 --> 00:37:16,300
Mr. Ma got eyes and ears everywhere.

388
00:37:17,300 --> 00:37:20,300
If we probe into it too much, he will be aware.

389
00:37:26,300 --> 00:37:30,300
There is another one that has eyes and ears everywhere like him.

390
00:37:31,300 --> 00:37:34,300
What would you like me to do for you? Please tell me.

391
00:37:35,300 --> 00:37:39,300
I know that you sell the secrets of Japanese soldiers.

392
00:37:41,300 --> 00:37:44,300
Oh, Big Brother, don't say that.

393
00:37:44,900 --> 00:37:47,300
I didn't sell anyone's secrets.

394
00:37:48,300 --> 00:37:52,300
Those who visit my place like to tell stories to my girls.

395
00:37:53,300 --> 00:37:55,300
And my girls like to talk.

396
00:37:55,700 --> 00:37:59,300
They just talk to one another, that's all.

397
00:37:59,800 --> 00:38:01,300
It's up to you. You can call what you like.

398
00:38:02,300 --> 00:38:03,300
I come here to day.

399
00:38:04,300 --> 00:38:06,300
Because I'd like you to help me check.

400
00:38:06,800 --> 00:38:08,300
Who do you want me to check?

401
00:38:08,700 --> 00:38:09,300
Jiu.

402
00:38:11,300 --> 00:38:12,300
The new worker Tian has just accepted for work.

403
00:38:14,300 --> 00:38:16,300
He once lived in Ma's area.

404
00:38:17,300 --> 00:38:21,300
You suspect if he is Ma's man?

405
00:38:21,900 --> 00:38:23,300
Don't ask too much.

406
00:38:24,300 --> 00:38:25,300
Just do what I want you to do.

407
00:38:26,300 --> 00:38:28,300
Don't let anyone know about this.

408
00:38:30,300 --> 00:38:31,300
All right, big brother.

409
00:38:32,300 --> 00:38:34,300
I will prove you

410
00:38:35,300 --> 00:38:38,300
how honest I am to you.

411
00:38:41,300 --> 00:38:45,300
But since you are here today,

412
00:38:48,300 --> 00:38:50,300
do you want me to take care of you?

413
00:38:59,300 --> 00:39:01,300
Don't do anything beyond my order.

414
00:39:02,300 --> 00:39:03,300
I let you investigate.

415
00:39:04,300 --> 00:39:06,300
Just do what I tell you, okay?

416
00:39:09,300 --> 00:39:11,300
You can trust me.

417
00:39:12,300 --> 00:39:14,300
I won't dare to do anything too much.

418
00:39:16,300 --> 00:39:17,300
I'm scared.

419
00:40:13,000 --> 00:40:14,000
Sir, Pin.

420
00:40:15,000 --> 00:40:18,000
Are you coming to inquire about the progress of the wedding?

421
00:40:19,000 --> 00:40:21,000
I'm about to let you know in the next two days.

422
00:40:21,500 --> 00:40:24,000
But I'm busy recently, I'm really sorry.

423
00:40:27,000 --> 00:40:28,000
Father.

424
00:40:31,000 --> 00:40:34,000
I've looked at two venues,

425
00:40:34,500 --> 00:40:36,000
but still can't decide which one.

426
00:40:37,000 --> 00:40:39,000
We should let the bride and groom choose.

427
00:40:45,000 --> 00:40:46,000
Aunt Li.

428
00:40:47,000 --> 00:40:48,000
What's the matter?

429
00:40:48,500 --> 00:40:50,000
I'd like to thank you a lot.

430
00:40:51,000 --> 00:40:56,000
Uncle Song and Aunt Li have supported our family all these years.

431
00:40:57,000 --> 00:40:59,000
You've been kind to me enough

432
00:40:59,600 --> 00:41:01,000
to let me engaged to Tian.

433
00:41:02,000 --> 00:41:04,000
But I really have to apologize.

434
00:41:09,000 --> 00:41:10,000
Apologize?

435
00:41:11,000 --> 00:41:12,000
Apologize for what?

436
00:41:13,000 --> 00:41:17,000
We come here today to break off the engagement.

437
00:41:17,700 --> 00:41:20,000
I would like to cancel the wedding of Tian and me.

438
00:41:26,000 --> 00:41:27,000
What is this, Sir?

439
00:41:35,000 --> 00:41:36,000
Madam.

440
00:41:38,000 --> 00:41:40,000
Madam, Madam.

441
00:41:41,000 --> 00:41:42,000
Madam Chan.

442
00:41:44,000 --> 00:41:45,000
We got big issue.

443
00:41:47,000 --> 00:41:48,000
I'm really sorry.

444
00:41:49,000 --> 00:41:51,000
I'm sorry that I cause the damage.

445
00:41:52,000 --> 00:41:54,000
But I really couldn't marry Tian.

446
00:41:54,500 --> 00:41:57,000
It's okay, Pin. I understand.

447
00:41:57,200 --> 00:41:58,000
But I don't understand.

448
00:42:01,000 --> 00:42:02,000
What is this, sir?

449
00:42:02,500 --> 00:42:05,000
Everything is already prepared.

450
00:42:05,500 --> 00:42:08,000
How can you ask for a cancellation as easily as a child's play like this?

451
00:42:09,000 --> 00:42:12,000
What about the debt and the mortgage for your palace you owe me?

452
00:42:15,000 --> 00:42:16,000
Aunt Li.

453
00:42:17,000 --> 00:42:18,000
Don't worry about that.

454
00:42:18,600 --> 00:42:21,000
I'm getting a lot of money from selling land.

455
00:42:22,000 --> 00:42:26,000
I'd like to repay the debt to buy back the palace with cash.

456
00:42:29,000 --> 00:42:30,000
Selling land?

457
00:42:43,000 --> 00:42:44,000
So it's like this.

458
00:42:51,000 --> 00:42:55,000
My elders have already recognized the wedding.

459
00:42:56,000 --> 00:42:58,000
I'll be embarrassed if you cancel the wedding like this.

460
00:42:58,500 --> 00:43:01,000
How am I going to tell these famous people?

461
00:43:01,200 --> 00:43:02,000
I won't accept this.

462
00:43:05,000 --> 00:43:07,000
If you don't agree, what can you do?

463
00:43:14,000 --> 00:43:18,000
Build a house, you have to please the dweller.

464
00:43:18,300 --> 00:43:20,000
They don't love each other.

465
00:43:20,500 --> 00:43:22,000
It's right to cancel the wedding.

466
00:43:25,000 --> 00:43:30,000
The wedding is canceled, so does the assignment ceremony, right?

467
00:43:30,300 --> 00:43:31,000
Sir.

468
00:43:32,000 --> 00:43:35,000
Chan, it's not something that you're going to talk about now.

469
00:43:36,000 --> 00:43:38,000
Mom, let's get out, it's not our business.

470
00:43:39,000 --> 00:43:40,000
How is it not?

471
00:43:40,300 --> 00:43:41,000
Yang.

472
00:43:41,100 --> 00:43:44,000
Don't tell me that Pin asked to cancel the wedding today

473
00:43:45,000 --> 00:43:46,000
because of you two.

474
00:43:48,000 --> 00:43:50,000
It's not relevant, Madam.

475
00:43:50,300 --> 00:43:51,000
Wait, calm down.

476
00:43:52,000 --> 00:43:53,000
It's my fault.

477
00:43:53,300 --> 00:43:55,000
See? I told you I wasn't involved in this.

478
00:43:55,500 --> 00:43:59,000
The heaven would just want to punish you.

479
00:43:59,400 --> 00:44:01,000
But you two are the ones who benefited.

480
00:44:02,000 --> 00:44:03,000
This is definitely not accidental.

481
00:44:03,300 --> 00:44:06,000
Nuan, take your master away.

482
00:44:06,500 --> 00:44:07,000
Madam, don't give up.

483
00:44:08,000 --> 00:44:09,000
I told you to leave.

484
00:44:09,000 --> 00:44:10,000
You must accept the truth, Madam.

485
00:44:11,000 --> 00:44:12,000
This is none of your business.

486
00:44:12,300 --> 00:44:14,000
It's none of your business, then it's mine.

487
00:44:14,500 --> 00:44:15,000
Enough!

488
00:44:17,000 --> 00:44:18,000
All of you!

489
00:44:20,000 --> 00:44:22,000
What's wrong with you?

490
00:44:23,000 --> 00:44:26,000
In front of me, in front of the guests, you still dare to argue.

491
00:44:29,000 --> 00:44:32,000
I'm sorry, Sir.

492
00:44:33,000 --> 00:44:37,000
This is a big issue. Please go back first.

493
00:44:38,000 --> 00:44:41,000
Let us consult and then we can talk later.

494
00:44:51,000 --> 00:44:54,000
You know about Pin selling the land right?

495
00:44:57,000 --> 00:44:59,000
I came across this notice in Tian's room.

496
00:45:00,000 --> 00:45:04,000
I'm still confused at first, but I got it now when Pin told us a moment ago.

497
00:45:06,000 --> 00:45:07,000
Yes.

498
00:45:08,000 --> 00:45:10,000
I'm the one who helps her sell the land.

499
00:45:12,000 --> 00:45:14,000
So she will have money to buy her palace back from Mother.

500
00:45:16,000 --> 00:45:17,000
Why did you do this?

501
00:45:18,000 --> 00:45:19,000
Tian.

502
00:45:21,000 --> 00:45:23,000
The elders who worked with the Five Dragons Association

503
00:45:23,700 --> 00:45:25,000
all know that you are going to get married.

504
00:45:27,000 --> 00:45:29,000
Five Dragons Association is not a small one.

505
00:45:30,000 --> 00:45:34,000
You can't just get married and end it like a child's play.

506
00:45:36,000 --> 00:45:40,000
Your engagement and wedding is canceled.

507
00:45:40,700 --> 00:45:43,000
It ruins our association's reputation.

508
00:45:43,200 --> 00:45:45,000
I've already told you.

509
00:45:46,000 --> 00:45:48,000
I don't want to get married.

510
00:45:49,000 --> 00:45:50,000
but no one listens to me

511
00:45:54,000 --> 00:45:55,000
Why don't you want to get married?

512
00:45:57,000 --> 00:45:58,000
Is Pin not good?

513
00:46:00,000 --> 00:46:02,000
Who do you love?

514
00:46:02,400 --> 00:46:04,000
Who do you want to marry? Tell me!

515
00:46:13,000 --> 00:46:14,000
Father.

516
00:46:17,000 --> 00:46:19,000
Tian is not involved in this. I'm the one who helps Pin.

517
00:46:22,000 --> 00:46:24,000
That's it, I knew it.

518
00:46:24,500 --> 00:46:26,000
You are like your mother

519
00:46:26,700 --> 00:46:27,000
seeking chance to destroy Tian.

520
00:46:28,000 --> 00:46:31,000
You probably team up your mom to destroy his wedding, right?

521
00:46:31,300 --> 00:46:32,000
Mother.

522
00:46:32,200 --> 00:46:33,000
Yang.

523
00:46:34,000 --> 00:46:37,000
It's you? Why did you do this?

524
00:46:38,000 --> 00:46:39,000
What else?

525
00:46:41,000 --> 00:46:42,000
He wants to inherit the position instead.

526
00:46:43,000 --> 00:46:46,000
Destroying Tian's wedding is the only way to buy the time.

527
00:46:46,400 --> 00:46:49,000
Mother, Yang is not such a person.

528
00:46:49,300 --> 00:46:51,000
I just don't want him to be forced.

529
00:46:52,000 --> 00:46:53,000
I feel sorry for him.

530
00:46:53,200 --> 00:46:54,000
Yang.

531
00:46:56,000 --> 00:46:57,000
Father. / Sir.

532
00:46:57,200 --> 00:46:58,000
Father. / Sir.

533
00:46:58,300 --> 00:46:59,000
Father.

534
00:47:00,000 --> 00:47:01,000
Let go of me.

535
00:47:03,000 --> 00:47:04,000
Do you want me to get the doctor?

536
00:47:04,300 --> 00:47:05,000
No.

537
00:47:06,000 --> 00:47:07,000
I just felt dizzy.

538
00:47:09,000 --> 00:47:10,000
I'm fine.

539
00:47:12,000 --> 00:47:13,000
I'll be better after sitting for a while.

540
00:47:25,000 --> 00:47:26,000
Li.

541
00:47:30,000 --> 00:47:31,000
Prepare to cancel the wedding

542
00:47:33,000 --> 00:47:36,000
and assignment of the new head of the association.

543
00:47:38,000 --> 00:47:40,000
We have to visit the elders

544
00:47:43,000 --> 00:47:44,000
